Package: albersdown
Type: Package
Title: Minimalist Theme and Vignette Kit for pkgdown and R Markdown
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Albersdown", family = "Authors", role = c("aut","cre"),
    email = "you@example.com"))
Description: A lightweight template package that standardizes pkgdown theming
    and provides an R Markdown vignette skeleton with local CSS, plus helper
    functions for ggplot2 and gt. Designed to be CRAN-friendly and easy to roll
    out across multiple packages.
URL: https://bbuchsbaum.github.io/albersdown/
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
